casebody.data:
MISCELLANEOUS ORDERS

2010-0360. In re Application of Carcione.

On April 27, 2010, counsel for applicant filed a motion to seal and a motion for clarification. Upon consideration thereof,

It is ordered by the court that the motions are denied.

Lundberg Stratton, J., would grant the motions. O’Donnell and Cupp, JJ., would grant the motion for clarification.
